data.description: Welcome to your private paradise where tranquility and comfort converge.  This ranch style home with open concept offers 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms.  Enjoy your vast wooded scenery with public amenities such as ATV trails, golfing, fishing and boating.  Features an attached garage that is 30x30.  Relax on the spacious front deck.  The basement is ready to be finished if you are looking for more space.  This property has deeded access to Lake Camelot with public access to Lake Petenwell and Lake Sherwood.  Seller is giving the buyer a $3000 flooring credit to give this property the finishing touches.
